1. Npm Install for Install in Package json
2. Already install mongodb 

Using PostMan: 

1. Open Postman
2. Choose the method (Get, POST, PUT (Edit) or Delete)
3. if want to login :
- fill email dan password in field
4. if want to fill data
- fill letter and frequency
5. if want to edit by id
- read data
- make a field (id)
- fill id in url
- fill the letter and frequency in the field

